WEBVTT

00:09:01.910 --> 00:09:03.433
He'd been kidnapped.

00:09:04.480 --> 00:09:05.741
He'd been tortured.

00:09:06.701 --> 00:09:10.909
And eyewitnesses say that his body
showed multiple wounds.

00:09:12.019 --> 00:09:13.197
Stab wounds.

00:09:15.838 --> 00:09:18.117
Two thousand miles away in Peshawar,

00:09:18.141 --> 00:09:24.553
Pakistani transgender activist Alisha
was shot multiple times in May 2016.

00:09:25.339 --> 00:09:27.375
She was taken to the hospital,

00:09:27.399 --> 00:09:29.574
but because she dressed
in women's clothing,

00:09:29.598 --> 00:09:33.950
she was refused access
to either the men's or the women's wards.